    <item>
      <title>联合国人权事务高级专员表示，必须切断缅甸军政府获取武器和现金的渠道</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-juntas-access-arms-cash-must-be-cut-off-un-rights-chief-says-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国人权事务高级专员周五表示，国际社会必须采取“有针对性的行动”，限制缅甸军政府获得武器、航空燃料和外汇，以防止其对其人民实施“暴行”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-juntas-access-arms-cash-must-be-cut-off-un-rights-chief-says-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 09:55:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸市场炮击造成12人死亡、80人受伤——叛军民兵</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/artillery-shelling-kills-12-myanmar-market-injures-80-rebel-militia-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在缅甸，炮弹落在若开邦西部一个繁忙的市场上，造成至少 12 名平民死亡，执政的军方和反军政府势力互相指责，指责该东南亚国家最近发生的暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/artillery-shelling-kills-12-myanmar-market-injures-80-rebel-militia-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 09:20:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚可能永久放弃对在海底电缆作业的外国船舶的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-reinstates-cabotage-waiver-foreign-ships-undersea-cable-repair-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚交通部长周五表示，马来西亚已决定推翻先前的决定，允许外国船只在其水域修复海底电缆，并补充称此举可能会永久化，以鼓励科技投资并支持数字经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-reinstates-cabotage-waiver-foreign-ships-undersea-cable-repair-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 07:49:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃克森美孚、壳牌与新加坡合作开展碳捕获和封存项目</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxonmobil-shell-work-with-singapore-carbon-capture-storage-project-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球能源巨头埃克森美孚和壳牌公司周五表示，将与新加坡合作开发跨境碳捕获和封存（CCS）项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxonmobil-shell-work-with-singapore-carbon-capture-storage-project-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 07:41:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：消息人士称德意志银行将对中国开发商世茂提起清算诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/deutsche-bank-file-liquidation-suit-against-chinese-developer-shimao-sources-say-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位消息人士称，德意志银行正准备在香港对中国开发商世茂集团提起清算诉讼，这是一家外国公司在信贷违约上升和中国房地产业危机加深之际采取的罕见举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/deutsche-bank-file-liquidation-suit-against-chinese-developer-shimao-sources-say-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 06:52:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人大将于下周推出更多刺激措施，但不太可能进行大胆改革</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-parliament-unveil-more-stimulus-next-week-bold-reforms-unlikely-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计中国人大将在周二开始的年度会议上公布温和的刺激计划，以稳定增长，但可能会让那些呼吁制定大胆政策详细路线图以解决该国深度结构性失衡的人感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-parliament-unveil-more-stimulus-next-week-bold-reforms-unlikely-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 06:10:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡空军将增加更多隐形战斗机，逐步淘汰旧式飞机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapores-air-force-add-more-stealth-fighters-it-phases-out-older-jets-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡国防部长本周表示，随着地区威胁的加剧，新加坡将再购买 8 架 F-35 隐形战斗机，最终取代其较旧的 F-16 战斗机，并使新加坡空军跻身“顶级联赛”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapores-air-force-add-more-stealth-fighters-it-phases-out-older-jets-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 06:09:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国重大工业事故发生的原因是什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/what-causes-bangladeshs-major-industrial-accidents-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国首都达卡一家印度香饭餐厅发生大火，烧毁一栋六层建筑，造成至少 44 人死亡、22 人重伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/what-causes-bangladeshs-major-industrial-accidents-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 05:21:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通选择汇丰银行和渣打银行在香港和台湾运营价值 5000 亿美元的托管业务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-picks-hsbc-stanchart-run-500-bln-custody-business-hong-kong-taiwan-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通发言人表示，摩根大通已选择汇丰银行和渣打银行在香港和台湾运营其托管业务，资产价值超过5000亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-picks-hsbc-stanchart-run-500-bln-custody-business-hong-kong-taiwan-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 04:02:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国尹表示，改善日本关系有助于遏制朝鲜威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-yoon-says-better-japan-ties-helping-deter-north-korea-threat-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈周五表示，改善与日本的关系有助于应对平壤武器开发的威胁，并呼吁国际社会帮助实现与朝鲜的统一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-yoon-says-better-japan-ties-helping-deter-north-korea-threat-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 03:44:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
